---
import Navbar from '../components/landing-clean/Navbar.astro';
import Hero from '../components/landing-clean/Hero.astro';
import Momentos from '../components/landing-clean/Momentos.astro';
import Proceso from '../components/landing-clean/Proceso.astro';
import Productos from '../components/landing-clean/Productos.astro';
import Personaliza from '../components/landing-clean/Personaliza.astro';
import Testimonios from '../components/landing-clean/Testimonios.astro';
import CTA from '../components/landing-clean/CTA.astro';
import Footer from '../components/landing-clean/Footer.astro';
---

<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/jpeg" href="/images/logo-valu-round.jpg" />
    <link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json" />

    <title>Valu Kraft | Papelería creativa y personalizados</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Valu Kraft: papelería creativa y productos personalizados hechos a mano para celebraciones inolvidables." />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://www.valukraft.com/" />
    <meta property="og:title" content="Valu Kraft" />
    <meta property="og:description" content="Papelería creativa hecha en Madrid con envíos a toda España para celebraciones memorables." />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://www.valukraft.com/" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://www.valukraft.com/images/logo-valu-round.jpg" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Navbar />
    <Hero />
    <Momentos />
    <Proceso />
    <Productos />
    <Personaliza />

    <section class="lk-reach" aria-labelledby="lkReachTitle">
      <div class="lk-reach__container">
        <span class="lk-reach__badge">Cobertura</span>
        <h2 id="lkReachTitle">Trabajamos en Madrid y enviamos a toda España</h2>
        <p>En Valu Kraft diseñamos y producimos de forma artesanal desde Madrid. Atendemos pedidos personalizados para clientes de toda España con seguimiento cercano en cada encargo.</p>
        <div class="lk-reach__chips">
          <span>Base operativa: Madrid</span>
          <span>Envíos nacionales</span>
          <span>Atención personalizada</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <Testimonios />
    <CTA />
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style is:global>
  :root {
    --background: hsl(30 33% 98%);
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    background: var(--background);
    color: #2f1f28;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
  }
  img { max-width: 100%; }
  a { transition: all .22s ease; }

  .lk-reach { padding: 24px 0 8px; }
  .lk-reach__container { max-width: 980px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
  .lk-reach__badge { display:inline-flex; border:1px solid #eadfdb; border-radius:999px; padding:6px 12px; font-size:.78rem; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:.08em; color:#8a6f61; background:#fff; }
  .lk-reach h2 { margin:12px 0 10px; font-family:'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size:clamp(1.5rem,4vw,2.2rem); color:#2f1f28; }
  .lk-reach p { margin:0; color:#6a5962; line-height:1.7; }
  .lk-reach__chips { margin-top:12px; display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; }
  .lk-reach__chips span { border:1px solid #eadfdb; border-radius:999px; padding:6px 10px; background:#fffaf7; color:#4b3842; font-size:.86rem; }
  @media (min-width:768px){ .lk-reach__container{ padding:0 32px; } .lk-reach { padding: 28px 0 10px; } }
</style>
